window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Kids can be such monsters. Literally. </p> <p>From the award-winning author of <i>Hidden Talents</i>, two remarkable short-story collections - <i>Kidzilla</i> and <i>The Witch's Monkey</i> - together for the first time. Plus several brand-new stories. Each hilarious and harrowing. </p> <p>A substitute teacher finds out she has some monsters for students. A group of kids attempts a levitation trick with hair-raising results. A neighborhood is so boring the grown-ups are turning into...well...you know. And dozens more.</p> <p>So don't be a weenie! Listen to these stories!</p>"; 
